      "a": "The federal government awarded $359M through HUBZone set-asides in FY2026 to date. There were 1,120 awards with an average award size of $321K, and obligations fell 60.9% year over year. Prior-year annual totals ranged from $938M in FY21 to $1.1B in FY23, with FY25 at $920M."
